{"type":"text","timestamp":1778378601088,"sessionID":"ses_1f0683152ffeCYT9xjnCqVwnXn","part":{"id":"prt_e0f9fed38001LQF0gTg31K3lYA","messageID":"msg_e0f9fe51c001sa1Zis8lsuMvV2","sessionID":"ses_1f0683152ffeCYT9xjnCqVwnXn","type":"text","text":"Existing GO has the requested parent `cargo receptor complex` defined with a logical pattern based on `protein-containing complex`, `capable_of cargo receptor activity`, and `part_of membrane`. For the new specific p24 complex, I’ll use a conservative asserted `is_a` to that parent plus a `capable_of_part_of` link to COPII cargo loading, avoiding a new logical definition that would overstate necessary and sufficient conditions for all p24 complexes.","time":{"start":1778378599736,"end":1778378601086},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0b6362ad8530d7b40169ffe767b188819fb6be538d6b986942","phase":"commentary"}}}}
